<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<Patch>

<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--  What this xml patch does:                                                                                       -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGAM_Apparel_SkitariiLegionnaireArmour from Skitarii Legionnaire Armour to Skitarii          -->
<!--       Legionnaire armour                                                                                         -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmour from imperial guard Flak Armor to Militarum Flak armour              -->
<!--      + Updates description to match                                                                              -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmourLight from light flak armour to Militarum light flak vest             -->
<!--      + Updates description to match                                                                              -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmourLightGreaves from light flak greaves to Militarum light flak pants    -->
<!--      + Updates description to match                                                                              -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGIG_Apparel_TempestusScion_CarapaceArmour from Tempestus Scion Carapace Armor to Tempestus  -->
<!--    Scion Carapace Armour                                                                                         -->
<!--      + Updates description to match                                                                              -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
    <Operation Class="PatchOperationFindMod">
        <mods>
            <li>Adeptus Mechanicus: Armoury</li>
        </mods>
        <match Class="PatchOperationSequence">
            <operations>

<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--        MECHANICUS APPAREL                                                                                        -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGAM_Apparel_SkitariiLegionnaireArmour from Skitarii Legionnaire Armour to Skitarii          -->
<!--       Legionnaire armour                                                                                         -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGAM_Apparel_SkitariiLegionnaireArmour"]/label</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <label>Skitarii Legionnaire armour</label>
                    </value>
                </li>

<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--        MILITARUM APPAREL                                                                                         -->
            </operations>
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmour from imperial guard Flak Armor to Militarum Flak armour              -->
<!--      + Updates description to match                                                                              -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmour"]/label</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <label>Militarum Flak armour</label>
                    </value>
                </li>

                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmour"]/description</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <description>Standard issue Flak armour for the Regiments of the Astra Militarum. It offers effective protection against all manner of attacks while remaining quite light.</description>
                    </value>
                </li>

<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmourLight from light flak armour to Militarum light flak vest             -->
<!--      + Updates description to match                                                                              -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmourLight"]/label</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <label>Militarum light flak vest</label>
                    </value>
                </li>

                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmourLight"]/description</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <description>A tough vest with armour plates sewn in. While it's not as good as solid armour, it offers effective protection against all manner of attacks while remaining quite comfortable.</description>
                    </value>
                </li>

<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmourLightGreaves from light flak greaves to Militarum light flak pants    -->
<!--      + Updates description to match                                                                              -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmourLightGreaves"]/label</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <label>Militarum light flak pants</label>
                    </value>
                </li>

                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGIG_Apparel_FlakArmourLightGreaves"]/description</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <description>A pair of pants with armour plates sewn in. While it's not as good as solid armour, it offers effective protection against all manner of attacks while remaining quite comfortable.</description>
                    </value>
                </li>

<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
<!--    + Sets label for OGIG_Apparel_TempestusScion_CarapaceArmour from Tempestus Scion Carapace Armor to Tempestus  -->
<!--    Scion Carapace Armour                                                                                         -->
<!--      + Updates description to match                                                                              -->
<!--  ==============================================================================================================  -->
                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGIG_Apparel_TempestusScion_CarapaceArmour"]/label</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <label>Tempestus Scion Carapace Armour</label>
                    </value>
                </li>

                <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
                    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="OGIG_Apparel_TempestusScion_CarapaceArmour"]/description</xpath>
                    <value>
                        <description>Carapace Armour is generally a sign of status and is mostly worn by Imperial officers and agents. Made from moulded plates of plasteel, ceramite, or other strong, light but highly resistant materials, it can cover the entire body or just selected regions of the body depending on the desired level of protection.\n\nTempestus Scions, for example, wear full-body suits of Carapace Armour, including an Omnishield Helm with a built-in targeting and imaging array, while most rank-and-file Astra Militarum soldiers are lucky to gain access to just a simple chestplate of Flak armour to wear over more comfortable mesh or flakweave suits. Some bodysuits have slots designed for simple carapace plates to be inserted in, so that the overall suits can be rapidly configured for as much or as little protection as desired. Damaged plates can in this way be more easily replaced without requiring the purchase of an entire new suit.</description>
                    </value>
                </li>

            </operations>
        </match>
    </Operation>
</Patch>
